      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 844810253,
      "version": 242,
      "versionNonce": 706592579,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774000674185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "n => number of nodes in list1\nm => number of nodes in list2\n\nwhile list1 and list2:\n\n        comparison (list1.val <= list2.val)      => O(1)  \n        assignment                               => O(1)  \n        move pointer                             => O(1) \n \n\nSo each iteration (constant time) ==> O(1)\n\nAt each iteration, only one node is processed (coming from either list1 or list2)\n    \n\n        Time Complexity: O(n + m)  ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "n => number of nodes in list1\nm => number of nodes in list2\n\nwhile list1 and list2:\n\n        comparison (list1.val <= list2.val)      => O(1)  \n        assignment                               => O(1)  \n        move pointer                             => O(1) \n \n\nSo each iteration (constant time) ==> O(1)\n\nAt each iteration, only one node is processed (coming from either list1 or list2)\n    \n\n        Time Complexity: O(n + m)  "
    },
